Naming
1 - AboutUsFragment, AboutUsActivity, AboutUsViewModel, AboutUsAdapter
2 - about_us_activity, about_us_fragment, about_us_item_view
3 - ids : userNameTv, passwordEt, sliderVp, profileImgv, nextBtn, rootViewCl, productsRv
4 - icons: ic_name, ic_name_white
5 - customDrawables: search_rounded_btn, about_us_et
6 - images: image_user_default.jpg, image_main_bg.jpg, image_login_bg.jpg
7 - strings: hint_name, label_name, error_name, success_name (default string file is arabic)


Screen arguments to be passed in actions (safe args) in navigation component
1 -  aboutUs : nothing
2 -  forgetPass : nothing
3 -  login : nothing
4 -  register : nothing
5 -  verification : (phoneNumber, userName, password)
6 -  cart : nothing
7 -  categories : nothing
8 -  contactUs: nothing
9 -  createProduct : nothing
10 - home : nothing
11 - myOrders : nothing
12 - myProducts : nothing
13 - notifications : nothing
14 - privacy : nothing
15 - product : (productId)
16 - products : (subCategoryId || searchParameters(to be identified later))
17 - profile : nothing
18 - reviews : (productId)
19 - writeReview : (productId)
20 - search : nothing
21 - splash : nothing
22 - subCategories : (categoryId)
23 - termsConditions : nothing
24 - MainActivity : nothing